OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fwith some patchy cloudy to the north.
OL,7,FLight winds may allow some mist to
OL,8,Fdevelop in spots. Feeling mild with
OL,9,Ftemperatures staying above average.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FBright and sunny throughout
OL,12,Fas high cloud moves northwards. Light
OL,13,Fwinds and strong sunshine will allow
OL,14,Ftemperatures to climb into the
OL,15,Fafternoon. Feeling hot in places.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,18,FRemaining dry with plenty of strong
OL,19,FJuly sunshine. Feeling hot by day with
OL,20,Fnights also turning increasingly warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
